You can not cast directly to `Map<String, String>`. The following program

```dart
import 'dart:convert';
void main() {
  dynamic value = json.decode('{"a": "b"}');
  print(value as Map<String, String>);
}
```

leads to 

```
Unhandled exception:
type '_InternalLinkedHashMap<String, dynamic>' is not a subtype of type 'Map<String, String>' in type cast
```

What about removing the double casts like this:

```dart
    dynamic value = json.decode('{"a": "b"}');
    print(value.cast<String, String>());
```

